image.altText: Lidia Thorpe protest

props.synopsis: The fallout from Lidia Thorpe’s message to the king has made global headlines. But what do Indigenous Australians make of the interaction? From 'Not really accurate' to 'very ballsy' First Nations people weigh in.

image.altText: Paradise Dam flawed

image.altText: Signage of Sydney's M2 toll motorway

props.synopsis: King Charles III and Queen Camilla's third and final official day of engagements in Australia will include stops at the Sydney Opera House and the Royal Australian Navy. Follow live.

image.altText: An exterior shot of a building with the Suncorp logo

image.altText: Composite image showing Charlie Stevens and Dhirren Randhawa.

image.altText: A microchip.

Our market has fallen sharply in early trade after a mixed lead from the US overnight.
